name: Thistlewhisker the Enchanted Squirrel
text: In the luminescent glade, Thistlewhisker scampered. Eyes glistened; a tiny heart fluttered with insatiable yearning. Sharp ivories nibbled on a radiant acorn, gracing her with arcane whispers of the forest. Shadows danced, her fluff a soft beacon. The moon smiled; Thistlewhisker, the sprite-squirrel, was the glen's secret keeper.
